==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌntə(r)|-ʌntə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A person who [[hunt]]s [[game]].
# A hunting dog.
# A hunting horse.
# A person who pursues someone.
#:''the '''hunter''' becomes the hunted.''
# A person who searches for something.

